<h2 id="what-is-makefile">What is makefile</h2>
<p>A <code>makefile</code> is a file containing a set of directives used by a <code>make</code> build automation tool to generate a target/goal.</p>
<p>You may have used make to compile a program from source code.</p>
<h2 id="how-to-write-makefile">How to write makefile</h2>
<p>To summarize, below is the syntax of a typical rule:</p>
